cast.overview: On the night of her college graduation, Natalie's life splits into parallel realities after she takes a pregnancy test. What will life and love bring?
cast.title: Look Both Ways

details.biography: Ashlyn Anderson is an actor, dancer and singer born in Garland, Texas to an acting family. She got her first film role at the age of five in the independent film, I Love You Because. She then was offered a small role in the short film, Clarity produced by Qico Films. Ashlyn loves acting on the stage and on film and dreams of being on Broadway in the future.
details.name: Ashlyn Anderson Gomez
